QuestData.Title: Chromie Time
QuestData.Description:
This... This is the Black Empire. We have traveled very far into the past, indeed.
Look! I see Ambassador Chronormu and Eternus! We need to hurry and complete the ritual.
Even my curiosity is not enough to wish to see where they might travel to next.
QuestData.LogDescription: Find Chromie and Complete the Temporal Stabilization Ritual.
QuestData.RewardText:
That feels much better!
Oh, don't worry about Eternus. We've come to a bit of a truce for the moment.
